Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn新宋体\fs8\fscy95\i1\bord0\shad3\c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H000000&\4a&H2C&\fad(800,700)\pos(310.8,147.4)}音 乐\N\N{\fs10.5}米夏尔·丹纳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}但在湿地里面 这里和那里...\N{\reng\i1}Then within the marsh, here and there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}才是真正的沼泽\N{\reng\i1}true swamp.
